{"tid":2097203,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"劉伯溫係唔係神棍","createTime":"2020-07-06T15:26:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T15:39:03.000Z","uid":105340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cb05b77008546785df51440fc2f3303fbad6575c","tid":2097203,"uid":105340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T15:26:49.000Z","msg":"十大預言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeddaef78d1a32db48930eeb16f29ca7689d121a","tid":2097203,"uid":105340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T15:39:03.000Z","msg":"劉伯溫預言：習近平滅中共建新政<br />\n十九佳人五五歲， 地靈人傑產新貴。<br />\n<br />\n解：「十九」等於「二十減一」。「二」和「十」合成一個「王」字，減去「一」成為「干」字，然後再加上「人」（兩撇）成為一個「平」字。「五五」指兩屆，一屆為五年。<br />\n<br />\n「地靈人傑」指沒有了共產黨的中國和國人。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />古代9UPPER 劉伯溫<br />\n從上下文來看，中國社會體制煥然一新，這裡的「產」應該指民選產生。「貴」指執政者。<br />\n<br />\n這段指一位姓名中帶「平」字之人將被民主選舉為新體制下的執政者，執政兩屆，一屆為五年。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}